#Text=2010 FIFA World Cup : arrivederci Italia !
#Text=Sunday , June 27 , 2010
#Text=Kamil Kopúnek 's late goal against Italy helped propel Slovakia into the round of 16 Image : Stefan Heinisch ( Flickr ) .
#Text=Slovakia eliminated defending champions
#Text=Italy from the World Cup .
#Text=First round groups E and F were decided on Thursday : Japan , Paraguay and the Netherlands progress alongside Slovakia .
#Text=When a team finishes third or fourth in a group , they are on their way home .
#Text=After the elimination of France , runners-up in 2006 , it was the turn of the reigning champions .
#Text=Slovakia met Italy in their first World Cup finals as an independent country .
#Text=After 81 minutes , the Azzuri ( Italy ) were down by two goals , both struck by Róbert Vittek , when they got one back .
#Text=They were denied a chance to equalize by a rebound from a Slovak knee on the goal line .
#Text=Their next goal was disallowed as offside .
#Text=The Slovaks strengthened their lead when a gross positioning error by Italy led to a goal from a corner .
#Text=Italy scored their second goal in the closing moments of the game , but it was n't enough , and the Azzuri were out of the tournament .
#Text=For the fourth time in history , the reigning world champion was eliminated in the first round .
#Text=The previous occasions were Italy in 1950 , Brazil in 1966 and France in 2002 .
#Text=Also on Thursday , Japan achieved a surprise 3 – 1 defeat of Denmark .
#Text=This , along with their victory over Cameroon on June 14 , secured their qualification .
#Text=Paraguay stamped their ticket for the round of sixteen in a nil – nil draw with New Zealand 's All Whites .
#Text=The draw gave New Zealand a point to take them ahead of Italy , finishing Group F in third place .
#Text=The All Whites leave the tournament undefeated , recalling Cameroon 's elimination in 1982 after three draws , pipped by Italy on goals scored .
#Text=The Netherlands beat Cameroon , securing Group E 's first place .
#Text=HAVE YOUR SAY Who do you tip to progress to the quarter finals ?
